I have very vivid memory of being a child in my grandparents' basement and watching some sort of a cartoon on the TV where a muscular hero was fighting a lamia demon that could shapeshift into anyone and as they were rolling on the ground it suddenly turned into him as he gasped.

For some reason that scene is still stuck in my mind, never figured out what the name of the cartoon was either even though I've tried to look it up, but I still remember it clearly. Imagine fighting your reflection, your image in your clone.
